### Get all users
GET https://localhost:7xxx/api/users
Authorization: Bearer valid-token-123

### Get user by ID
GET https://localhost:7xxx/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer valid-token-123

### Create new user
POST https://localhost:7xxx/api/users
Authorization: Bearer valid-token-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

### Update user
PUT https://localhost:7xxx/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer valid-token-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "phone": "+0987654321"
}

### Delete user
DELETE https://localhost:7xxx/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer valid-token-123

### Test without authentication (should return 401)
GET https://localhost:7xxx/api/users

### Test with invalid data (should return 400)
POST https://localhost:7xxx/api/users
Authorization: Bearer valid-token-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "invalid-email"
}